Copyright (c) 2026 LDC Labs

This repository provides an agent-agnostic *runtime adapter* for running the
LongDS-Bench benchmark with the agent under test acting as the runtime. The
original code in this repository (the scripts and documentation authored here)
is licensed under the MIT License (see LICENSE).

